@mirle234 - To me, SPARGE means to bubble a gas through a liquid. I would often have to deoxygenate seawater and other solutions and I did so by SPARGing with pure nitrogen. I would also do the opposite: oxygenate a solution by SPARGing with air or pure oxygen. 

